===Etymology===
The {{zh-ref|Baxter and Sagart (2014)}} reconstruction of this word is {{m|und|*s-tˤəŋ}}, suggesting the word is derived from {{och-l|登|tr=*tˤəŋ|to go up}} by {{m|und|*s-}} prefixing.

